}, {\"ngram\": \"the time trial\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has won two of cycling's five monument races and it is not unfathomable that he might one day complete the set, something only three riders have ever done.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cycling's five monument races\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the set\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"only three riders\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those is the great Eddy Merckx, the fellow Belgian Evenepoel is so often compared to, and with good reason.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2913, \"end\": 2924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddy_Merckx\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1961734779814565e-65, \"text\": \"Eddy Merckx\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddy_Merckx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddy_Merckx\"}, {\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9972631080383573, \"rank\": 0.0027443718547404163, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good reason\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remco Evenepoel (Belgium) 6:19:34 2.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Remco Evenepoel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Remco_Evenepoe